          <summary>Versailles or Disneyland for the day trip?</summary>
          <p>Versailles is culture + gardens. Disneyland is full-day entertainment. Pick one.</p>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>What should I book first?</summary>
          <p>Book Louvre, Eiffel, Orsay, then your day trip choice (Versailles or Disneyland). Add extras after anchors are locked.</p>
        </details>
